name: ZOINKS
description:
ZOINKS.
Quick timing and reflexes is what you will need,
Or you will be saying more than ZOINKS.
Tap left of screen to DUCK, and Tap right of screen to JUMP.
5 challenging Game Rooms to play and test your skills, all with different style game play.
Collect CD's to unlock new characters to play with.

-5 Rooms-
Chill Room
Funk Room
Hype Room
Psyche Room
Zoink Room
